description:
An original convict-built building is lovingly restored. 
Through thoughtful conservation, this structure is not merely "brought back to life", as the life under which it was constructed was brutal beyond anything we can imagine today!
With compassionate vision it is given new life which incorporates the strength and determination of the past, along with our modern-day gratitude and sensitivity to the hardships suffered by the convicts, well into the future.
